	(32,'4','2013-05-10 11:28:24',1,'2013-05-10 01:43:03','Nutrition Info',1,'<p>What an exciting new area for RPG members!&nbsp; You will find the following information:</p><table style=\"width: 750px;\" border=\"0\" cellspacing=\"4\" cellpadding=\"4\" bgcolor=\"#FFFFFF\"><tbody><tr><td width=\"250\"><h4 align=\"center\"><a href=\"/nutrition-info/info-for-professionals.html\"><img style=\"vertical-align: middle; margin-right: 4px; margin-left: 4px;\" title=\"nutrition info for professionals\" src=\"/files/images/professional_resources.jpg\" alt=\"nutrition info for professionals\" width=\"200\" /></a><br /><a href=\"/nutrition-info/info-for-professionals.html\">Info for Professionals</a></h4></td><td width=\"250\"><h4 align=\"center\"><a href=\"/nutrition-info/links-resources.html\"><img style=\"vertical-align: middle; margin-right: 4px; margin-left: 4px;\" title=\"links and rexources\" src=\"/files/images/links_resources.jpg\" alt=\"links and resources\" width=\"200\" /></a><a href=\"/nutrition-info/links-resources.html\">Links &amp; Resources</a></h4></td><td width=\"250\"><h4 align=\"center\"><a href=\"/nutrition-info/info-for-consumers.html\"><img style=\"vertical-align: middle; margin-right: 4px; margin-left: 4px;\" title=\"nutrition info for consumers\" src=\"/files/images/consumer_resources.jpg\" alt=\"nutrition info for consumers\" width=\"200\" /></a><br /><a href=\"/nutrition-info/info-for-consumers.html\">Info for Consumers</a></h4></td></tr><tr><td><h4 align=\"center\">&nbsp;<a href=\"/nutrition-info/renal-disease-apps.html\"><img src=\"/files/images/renal_appl.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></a><br /><a href=\"/nutrition-info/renal-disease-apps.html\">Renal Disease Apps</a></h4></td><td><h4 align=\"center\">&nbsp;<a href=\"/nutrition-info/academy-updates.html\"><img style=\"vertical-align: middle; margin-right: 4px; margin-left: 4px;\" title=\"Academy Updates\" src=\"/files/images/academy.jpg\" alt=\"Academy Updates\" width=\"200\" /></a><a href=\"/nutrition-info/acade